{"tid":1553572,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[文宣] 聽朝一定要去廣傳呢2單新聞︰稱呼長者們為「曱甴」 + 亂向行人投擲彈","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T17:09:31.000Z","uid":54684,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"001f37ed0d5d267ba18f07d245c90164f6307edd","tid":1553572,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:54:42.000Z","msg":"(1)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2439252582810090?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F2439252582810090%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=0bf00b6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2439252582810090?sfns=mo</a><br />\n【旺角即時】於警方進行清場期間，有警員多次以警棍指罵「守護孩子」成員，更疑似稱呼長者們為「曱甴」。<br />\n有在場記者多番勸喻警方，指「守護孩子」成員皆為長者，請大家互相尊重、不要欺負及指罵伯伯。惟警察一方並沒有聽從，反指「係鍾意篤呀點呀」及稱「冇話伯唔伯」。<br />\n<br />\n(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100024989259349/posts/476254706550834?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100024989259349%2Fposts%2F476254706550834%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=ea2f1c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100024989259349/posts/476254706550834?sfns=mo</a><br />\n亂向行人投擲彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykhZ4O1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykhZ4O1.gif&h=0c743e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>AIRDROP or POSTERS</strong>"},{"pid":"55ac482557493bb8cce68ee488942c0ae16668d3","tid":1553572,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 